prompts.frontCover: My-person-1 is on the left and my-person-2 is on the right. Minimalist 2D cartoon illustration for a greeting card front. A funny and charming scene is set on a calm, sandy beach. Lao Lao and Jordan are sitting cross-legged on a large beach blanket, facing each other with joyful, laughing expressions. Between them, a long surfboard rests on the sand, repurposed as a picnic table. On the surfboard are several stacked bamboo steamers, one open to reveal delicious dim sum, and two steaming mugs of coffee. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and Jordan is wearing a tan hoodie, mirroring their clothes from the photo. A few curious, cartoonish seagulls stand around them on the sand, each wearing a comically tiny white chef's hat. The background is simple with soft, muted tones of sand, gentle blue ocean waves, and a clear sky. Centered in the middle of the card, in an elegant, readable handwritten cursive script, the text says "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao". Clean lines, flat colors, simple shapes, and a bright, airy feel.
